text: Hana Žáková (born 29 September 1974) is a Czech rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Czech female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Prague
